.DS_Store
*.app/
*.bak

# update-signing private keys must NEVER be committed (they live offline, e.g.
# ~/.config/printer-keepalive/update.md). Belt-and-suspenders even though
# they're out of tree. NOTE: the signing key uses a .md extension, so block its
# exact name explicitly — we can't ignore all *.md (README.md etc. are tracked).
*.key
*.pem
update.md
update.key
